SEARCH
模块 jmc.utils
程序包 com.jmc.lang

类 BuiltIns

java.lang.Object
com.jmc.lang.BuiltIns
public class BuiltIns extends Object
Java内置函数
从以下版本开始:
3.8
API Note:

 import static com.jmc.lang.Builtins.*;

 // In JDK 21
 void main() {
     print(666);
     println();
     printf("%d + %d = %d\n", 3, 4, 3 + 4);

     println(sqrt(9));
     println(pow(2, 5));
     println(round(3.4f));
     println(round(4.7d));
     println(abs(-3));
     println(max(3, 4));
     println(min(-1, 2));
 }
